headline: MarketAxess to Host Conference Call Announcing First Quarter 2025 Financial Results on Wednesday, May 7, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, April 16, 2025--MarketAxess Holdings Inc. (Nasdaq: MKTX) the operator of a leading electronic trading platform for fixed-income securities, will issue a press release announcing its first quarter 2025 financial results on Wednesday, May 7, 2025, before the market opens.
